data.description:
Welcome to 5189 US 12 in Three Oaks, MI - just under an hour and a half commute from Chicago! Come see the Cape Cod with 4 beds/3 FULL bathrooms on a full basement with potential to finish, a screened in porch to take in all the views, a FOUR-car garage, solar panel system- All on a very sufficient 17.76 acres. UPDATES INCLUDE: Roof; 2015, NEW AC compressor 2023, Furnace 2013, NEW well 2018, newer windows, light fixtures, toilets and carpet in living room. New appliances
Nestled in a great location away from the road, this property offers tranquility in its walking trails cut through the woods, teeming with wildlife. Enjoy the picturesque views of the sun rising in the east through the massive picture window in the living room and then finish the day in the screened-in porch with even more idyllic views of the sun setting in the west. With easy access to local amenities and nearby attractions in Three Oaks, this home presents ideal potential for comfortable living. Don't miss out on making this your new nature haven!
